divs: sighting detailshere is a still shot from white tank mountains arizona webcam on 11\27\2007 at 9:30am. there were three unknown objects in the sky and one close to the ground. more objects are in the still shot just before this one has objects near the mountain and one looks to be close to the shape of the object near the ground. i have analyzed this photo inside and out and its not a duck or bird due to many factors including distance size and proportion. there are webcams all over the world and its almost impossible to watch them all so i stay with some of the good ones.
